
## 2016 Mercedes-Benz Challenge season

The 2016 Mercedes-Benz Challenge is the sixth season of the Mercedes-Benz Challenge.

# Entry list 

CLA AMG Cup drivers compete utilising the Mercedes-Benz CLA AMG while C250 Cup drivers use the Mercedes-Benz C250. All drivers were Brazilian-registered, excepting Jo√£o Lemos, who raced under Portuguese racing license.

# Race calendar and results 

All races were held in Brazil.

